<h2>Connect Your Binance Account</h2>

<div class="card mb-4">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h4>How to create a Binance API key</h4>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <ol>
      <li>Log in to your Binance account</li>
      <li>Go to <strong>Profile</strong> > <strong>API Management</strong></li>
      <li>Create a new API key</li>
      <li>Label it "Tramate" or similar so you know what it's for</li>
      <li>Enable "Enable Reading" and "Enable Spot & Margin Trading" permissions</li>
      <li>For enhanced security, restrict API access to specific IP addresses</li>
      <li>Do not enable withdrawal permissions</li>
      <li>Copy both the API key and Secret key</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h4>Enter Your API Credentials</h4>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <%= render 'form', api_credential: @api_credential %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-3">
  <%= link_to 'Back to API Connections', api_credentials_path %>
</div>
